<% title 'Registration Requests' %>

<h1>Request Approval Result:</h1>

<% if @exception_trace.present? %>

  An error occurred. You might want to check the code of demands.rb, in method after_approval().
  <p>

  <div class="flash_error"><pre><%= @exception_trace %></pre></div>

<% elsif @info.present? %>
  The account request was approved, and the user was successfully created:
  <div class="flash_notice"><pre><%= @info %></pre></div>

<% end %>

<p>

You can go <%= link_to "back to see the request", demand_path(@demand) %>.<br/>
You can go <%= link_to "back to the request list", :action => :index %>.

